title: Lower Level Duplex in Como-8/1/22 Move-in
posting_body: ['Spacious 6 bedroom lower level of this duplex for rent in Como near the University of Minnesota, Twin Cities campus for the 2022-2023 school year!', 'It comes equipped with 2 bathrooms, a fully-equipped kitchen, large living room, washer and dryer in-unit, and it’s pet friendly (no pet rent or pet deposits!).', ' This home is available for the 2022-2023 school year.', 'You can also have this house as an easy and affordable 5 bedroom plus den/office.', ' Free off-street parking and plenty of room for bikes.', 'The lease begins on August 1, 2022 and will run until August 24, 2023.', 'Contact me with any questions or to set-up a showing!', 'Students will receive 1/2 off their security deposit and no application fee with a student ID!', 'Renters are responsible for setting up and managing electric and gas.', 'For showings, questions, or further inquiries contact Marisa (612.500.34two.six, texting preferred) or reply to ad.']
